PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of NEW BRUNSWICK, namely the Hon. PATRICIA L. CUMMING, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from November 5 to November 9, 1995, inclusive, during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
